With my current situation with acne I wanted something to make my skin back to where it was! And Hyphen came up with their new “Anti-acne” range!🩵🩵🩵 @letshyphen 
I was super excited & definitely wanted to try all the products in their range🩵

My skin is not only acne-prone but also sensitive and this range has helped me combat acne and helped to keep it under control!

There are 3 products in this range:
- Clarifying Acne Cleanser 
- Acne Defence Daily Serum
- Acne Fix Spot Corrector

All these products worked well with my skin & helped me to get my smooth skin texture back!
And if there’s new acne popping, I apply the “Acne Fix Spot Corrector” to help it shrink.

Overall it’s an amazing range, & you can definitely give it a try🩵🩵🩵

@kritisanon @letshyphen 
#NoMorePopping #AcneSaviour #letshyphen #acnecare
